{"tid":1439434,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生比啲骨氣，咪撚再補P Chan呢條友！","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T15:29:49.000Z","uid":24554,"like":185,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"faf5e31b8a3d47412961cdf76d74f016567c32fe","tid":1439434,"uid":24554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"各位中學生要補習都唔好搵P Chan補啦<br />\n<br />\n條友上summer 第四堂個陣<br />\n陰啲陰啲係度唱衰示威者<br />\n係度講咩：外國人眼中香港既暴動愈來愈多啦<br />\nHong King is ripe with violence<br />\n啲暴力人士愈來愈猖獗啦<br />\n香港既和諧就係比愈來愈多既暴力破壞左啦<br />\n香港最近真係好多暴動<br />\n<br />\n作為補習名師，都唔係要求你利用自己名氣去做啲乜<br />\n但不停同啲學生唱衰示威者真係好撚賤<br />\n<br />\n坊間仲有好多教得唔錯既英文補習老師<br />\n唔使補佢🤗<br />\n<br />\n（一手，已fact check）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z11jSh1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz11jSh1.png&h=0b9c1871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7714748a1b3d3357c2cf80e832ccf92fd25f1c9e","tid":1439434,"uid":128509,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"教畜"},{"pid":"98a84fd9f1398cd6030101694214478d5c2e821f","tid":1439434,"uid":61667,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"仲有林溢欣<br />\n<br />\n一個講一套做一套的偽君子"},{"pid":"c103e17c53300e2130ba17999ade0cac25902147","tid":1439434,"uid":303696,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"印象中佢有出嚟行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5244033c7c2b946770e5575d5545a0591dd37617","tid":1439434,"uid":57378,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"作為補習名師，都唔係要求你利用自己名氣去做啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前唔係你哋好叻叫人哋表態㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bd2e05e162125532d26d747aa92bb66e2b9bb8","tid":1439434,"uid":230239,"like":103,"